OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few heavy showers at first,
OL,6,Fperhaps thundery at times, these soon
OL,7,Fclearing east in the morning.
OL,8,FOtherwise cool, dull and cloudy with
OL,9,Fsome patchy light drizzle possible.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FStaying dull and cloudy
OL,12,Fthrough the evening and overnight with
OL,13,Fperhaps some patchy light drizzle in
OL,14,Fplaces. A few clearer spells may
OL,15,Fdevelop towards Fraserburgh and
OL,16,FPeterhead towards morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
