OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA largely cloudy start though
OL,6,Fperhaps some brightness towards the
OL,7,Fnortheast. Brightening up for all
OL,8,Fthrough the day with sunny intervals
OL,9,Fdeveloping. A bit warmer than Saturday.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,12,Fto Wednesday dry with sunny spells,
OL,13,Fsome overnight cloud or fog. Becoming
OL,14,Fwarm or very warm inland but staying
OL,15,Fcooler around the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
